# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AI Readiness Check - Environment Configuration
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Supabase Configuration
# Get these values from: https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/YOUR_PROJECT/settings/api
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# Instructions:
# 1. Create a Supabase project at https://supabase.com
# 2. Go to Project Settings > API
# 3. Copy the "Project URL" to VITE_SUPABASE_URL
# 4. Copy the "anon public" key to VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
# 5. Rename this file to .env

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI Hub Configuration (Server-Side Only)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# IMPORTANT: The adesso AI Hub API key is NOT stored in this file!
# 
# For security reasons, the API key is stored in Supabase Secrets
# and accessed only by the Edge Function (server-side).
#
# To configure the AI Hub API key:
#
# 1. Install Supabase CLI: npm install -g supabase
# 2. Login: supabase login
# 3. Link your project: supabase link --project-ref YOUR_PROJECT_REF
# 4. Set the secret:
#    supabase secrets set ADESSO_AI_HUB_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
#
# 5. Deploy the Edge Function:
#    supabase functions deploy ai-proxy
#
# The frontend calls the Edge Function, which securely adds the API key
# before forwarding requests to the AI Hub. This prevents API key exposure
# in the browser/JavaScript bundle.
#
# Architecture:
# ┌─────────────────┐     ┌──────────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐
# │  React App      │────▶│  Supabase Edge       │────▶│  adesso AI Hub  │
# │  (gh-pages)     │     │  Function (ai-proxy) │     │  API            │
# │                 │◀────│  [API Key in secrets]│◀────│                 │
# │  No API key!    │     │                      │     │                 │
# └─────────────────┘     └──────────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────